09:18.811 --> 09:19.372
Yeah.

09:19.392 --> 09:24.318
Where you are artistic, where you have... Oh, that's wonderful.

09:24.338 --> 09:25.279
You're going to give us this?

09:25.639 --> 09:25.740
Yeah.

09:25.760 --> 09:28.883
