09:40.938 --> 09:41.599
They're beautiful.

09:42.601 --> 09:42.981
You know, like...

09:43.417 --> 09:44.238
Reminders.

09:45.839 --> 09:46.380
Still here?

09:51.364 --> 09:56.469
The villa where Helen was standing on the balcony with the tiara.

09:56.489 --> 10:03.795
That's gorgeous.

10:03.815 --> 10:06.037
I guess this question would really be my last one.

10:06.077 --> 10:11.982
If there's anything else I need, I'll call you.

10:12.002 --> 10:12.883
I guess I was

10:13.167 --> 10:16.834
kind of probing the getting close to the creative process thing.

10:17.455 --> 10:33.864
Those are favorite places.

10:34.525 --> 10:37.150
See, now this is the American church in Rome.

10:38.210 --> 10:40.493
The interior was done by Morris and Company.

10:40.513 --> 10:42.335
