pamphlets were so fragile that to have them all here is it a legacy for you do you think had you had you thought when you started collecting that you would be creating i didn't even remember the preface well i no i didn't know the collection i know that but i'm saying now i'm saying oh now yeah i mean i know i'm not saying that when you ever start i'm saying now i mean when we look at the

